{
  "stem": "5375.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he told me, 'Don't you ever-- if they are going to take you into the battle line, and you are going to come to Russia on the eastern front, don't you ever try to go through in prison.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they didn't let me, only two years later, after the war, to come home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They keep you, and they are working with you, and they are taking you to Siberia, and so on and so on,' he says.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I kept that in my mind, my father's teaching, and I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was running with the other ones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I tried to make myself useful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't complain.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was times when we really were very, very hungry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the-- the army, they couldn't bring food for them, and for us, neither.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they'd rather feed them than us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were not so valuable than the-- the soldier who was fighting the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were digging out the potatoes where the farmer plant potatoes into the ground.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were digging them out, and we were eating them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The farmer couldn't say a word, because they went, and they took away their cattle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They took away everything else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So they were afraid to say anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, we came through into former Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then really, we started running.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because then they were pushing us, and pushing us even further.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was all summer long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were working here a little bit, working there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some people ran away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had a friend of mine in Budapest, where I used to live, my landlady's brother I met over there, in the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we kept ourselves together until the Russians were behind us about 15 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
